judge :: Array (Int,Int) Int -> (Int,Int) -> Bool
judge a p@(i,j) = row && col && blk
  where
    v = a ! p
    row = (==1) . length . filter (==v) $ [a ! (i,k) | k <- [0..8]]
    col = (==1) . length . filter (==v) $ [a ! (k,j) | k <- [0..8]]
    blk = (==1) . length . filter (==v) $ [a ! (k,l) | k <- [ii..ii+2], l <- [jj..jj+2]]
    ii = 3 * div i 3
    jj = 3 * div j 3

    index << next_i

def checker(line)
  line_checker = []
  line.each do |l|
    if (mistakes = l.uniq.select{|i| l.index(i) != l.rindex(i)}).any?
      temp = []
      mistakes.each do |mistake|
        temp << get_all_index(l, mistake)
      end
      line_checker << temp.flatten
    end
  end
  line_checker
end

    [1,4,7].each do |j|
      cb = []
      cb_index = []
      box_index.each do |b|
        cb_index << [b[0] + i, b[1] + j]
        cb << puzzle[b[0] + i][b[1] + j]
      end
      if (temp = cb.uniq.select{ |x| cb.index(x) != cb.rindex(x) }).any?
        temp.each do |m|
          get_all_index(cb, m).each do |i|
            x, y = cb_index[i]
            errata[x][y] = false
          end
        end
      end
    end
  end

  # output
  0.upto(8) do |i|
    0.upto(8) do |j|
      if errata[i][j]
        print " #{puzzle[i][j]}"
      else
        print "*#{puzzle[i][j]}"
      end
      puts "" if j == 8
    end
  end

  virgin = false if virgin
end
